In the following folders you will find what is needed to reproduce the results obtained in the study: "TODO: updated Title".

./mapping           : contains mapping alignments (sorted BAM) of uniquely mapped reads
./assembly          : contains de novo assembly results obtained by MIRA v3.4.0 (ACE files)
./assemblyvariants  : contains SNP and InDel variants detected by SeqSphere+ and the corresponding R script to visualize these results in Venn diagrams
./reads             : contains raw, trimmed and sub-sampled reads generated in the course of this study. 
./references        : the genomic reference sequences used
./scripts           : scripts used to process and analyse the sequencing data split into corresponding subfolders



